 <text>
  <front>
   <head>THE MODERN PATRIOT.</head>
  </front>
  <body>
   <lg xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" type="poem">
    <lg n="1" stanza_type="quatrain">
     <l n="1" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">REBELLION is my theme all day,</l>
     <l n="2" met="-+|-+|-+" line_length="6">I only wish 'twould come</l>
     <l n="3" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">(As who knows but perhaps it may)</l>
     <l n="4" met="-+|-+|-+" line_length="6">A little nearer home.</l>
    </lg>
    <lg n="2" stanza_type="quatrain">
     <l n="5" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">Yon roaring boys who rave and fight</l>
     <l n="6" met="-+|-+|-+" line_length="6">On t'other side the Atlantic,</l>
     <l n="7" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">I always held them in the right,</l>
     <l n="8" met="-+|-+|-+" line_length="6">But most so, when most frantic.</l>
    </lg>
    <lg n="3" stanza_type="quatrain">
     <l n="9" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">When lawless mobs insult the court,</l>
     <l n="10" met="-+|-+|-+" line_length="6">That man shall be my toast,</l>
     <l n="11" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">If breaking windows be the sport</l>
     <l n="12" met="-+|-+|-+" line_length="6">Who bravely breaks the most.</l>
    </lg>
    <lg n="4" stanza_type="quatrain">
     <l n="13" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">But oh! for him my fancy culls</l>
     <l n="14" met="-+|-+|-+" line_length="6">The choicest flow'rs she bears,</l>
     <l n="15" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">Who constitutionally pulls</l>
     <l n="16" met="-+|-+|-+" line_length="6">Your house about your ears.</l>
    </lg>
    <lg n="5" stanza_type="quatrain">
     <l n="17" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">Such civil broils are my delight,</l>
     <l n="18" met="-+|-+|-+" line_length="6">Tho' some folks can't endure 'em,</l>
     <l n="19" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">Who say the mob are mad outright,</l>
     <l n="20" met="-+|-+|-+" line_length="6">And that a rope must cure 'em.</l>
    </lg>
    <lg n="6" stanza_type="quatrain">
     <l n="21" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">A rope! I wish we patriots had</l>
     <l n="22" met="-+|-+|-+" line_length="6">Such strings for all who need 'em â€”</l>
     <l n="23" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">What! hang a man for going mad?</l>
     <l n="24" met="-+|-+|-+" line_length="6">Then farewell British freedom.</l>
    </lg>
   </lg>
